蹲能蹲110kg因为一开始不太会…<a class="toggle-expand inline" href="/question/268275961/answer/335722670">显示全部</a></div><div class="visible-expanded"><div class="zm-item-vote-info" data-votecount="270"><span class="voters"><span class="member"><a href="/people/tang-zhi-yuan-73" data-hovercard='p$t$tang-zhi-yuan-73'>唐智圆</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/neng-zhe-70" data-hovercard='p$t$neng-zhe-70'>94年的蟹蟹</a><span>、</span></span><span class="member"><a href="/people/ran-xiao-25-74" data-hovercard='p$t$ran-xiao-25-74'>冉晓</a></span></span> <a class="more">等人赞同</a></div><script type="text" class="content"><p>从大一下学期开始健身吧，一开始是想要多做力量训练锻炼身体，顺带降低一下体脂的，所以偶尔也去打球。后来开始主要练力量举三项 卧推深蹲和硬拉。 <br>我力量基础还不错可能和初高中就喜欢运动有关系吧，一开始卧推就能推70kg，深蹲能蹲110kg因为一开始不太会硬拉所以没测过不知道能拉多少…<br>去年深蹲210kg  硬拉260kg<br><br>195kg 3个3组<br><br><br><br><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/954503575334850560" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic7.zhimg.com/v2-ee0c2119069e34e46ebc133023974450.jpg" data-lens-id="954503575334850560">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic7.zhimg.com/v2-ee0c2119069e34e46ebc133023974450.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="z-ico-extern-gray"></span><span class="z-ico-extern-blue"></span></span>                <span class="url"><span class="z-ico-video"></span>https://www.zhihu.com/video/954503575334850560</span>              </span>            </a><br><br><br><br>硬拉260kg<br><a class="video-box" href="//link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.zhihu.com/video/954503765798215680" target="_blank" data-video-id="" data-video-playable="" data-name="" data-poster="https://pic7.zhimg.com/v2-71359246fe55e7bcc0559f0a8853883e.jpg" data-lens-id="954503765798215680">              <img class="thumbnail" src="https://pic7.zhimg.com/v2-71359246fe55e7bcc0559f0a8853883e.jpg"><span class="content">                <span class="title"><span class="